  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_f158765e3b89db27376c5ef810bc31e0">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Lectures in various topics related to biology and society, including the biology of man, man's diseases, agriculture, technology, economics, medicine, vision and perception, and computers.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_46d21f7caba090716f86307ce7b7e94d">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Also, transcripts of taped lectures by Richard D. O'Brien on "Psychoactive Drugs," May 9, 1970; Robert S. Morison on "Experimentation on People," January 29, 1973; and Karen Arms on  "Development of Sexuality," March 12, 1973.</p>  </scopecontent>
